---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import FloatingContactWidget from '../components/forms/FloatingContactWidget.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Nasofibrolaringoscopia" description="Servicio de nasofibrolaringoscopia en CMEO Especialistas - Diagnostico de vias respiratorias superiores">

  <!-- Hero Section with Image -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="https://cmeo.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/ss1.png"
        alt="Nasofibrolaringoscopia"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/40 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 w-full pb-12 pt-32 px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white/90 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
          </svg>
          Procedimiento Diagnostico
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight">
          Nasofibrolaringoscopia
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Diagnostico avanzado de vias respiratorias superiores
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="relative py-16 lg:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white">
    <!-- Decorative Elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-brand-green-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative">
      <!-- Introduction Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-soft-xl border border-gray-100/80 p-8 lg:p-12 mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green-500 to-brand-green-600 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 shadow-green-glow">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Bienvenido a nuestro Centro Medico</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Nos complace ofrecerte nuestro servicio de nasofibrolaringoscopia, una herramienta diagnostica fundamental en el campo de la otorrinolaringologia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          La nasofibrolaringoscopia es un procedimiento endoscopico no invasivo que nos permite examinar detalladamente las vias respiratorias superiores, incluyendo la nariz, la faringe y la laringe. Utilizando un endoscopio flexible de alta resolucion y una luz brillante, podemos obtener imagenes claras y detalladas de estas estructuras internas.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Durante el procedimiento, introducimos cuidadosamente el endoscopio a traves de la nariz, lo que permite una visualizacion directa de la cavidad nasal y las areas circundantes. Esto nos permite evaluar la mucosa nasal, los cornetes, el tabique nasal y cualquier otra estructura que pueda estar causando obstruccion o dificultades respiratorias.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features Grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-soft-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green-50 to-brand-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">No Invasivo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Procedimiento sin cirugia ni anestesia general</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-soft-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue-50 to-brand-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Diagnostico Preciso</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Imagenes de alta resolucion en tiempo real</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-soft border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-soft-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-pink-50 to-brand-pink-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-brand-pink-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Rapido y Comodo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Realizable en consulta externa</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Detailed Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-green-50/50 to-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 border border-brand-green-100/50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-green-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.228 9c.549-1.165 2.03-2 3.772-2 2.21 0 4 1.343 4 3 0 1.4-1.278 2.575-3.006 2.907-.542.104-.994.54-.994 1.093m0 3h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Que podemos diagnosticar?</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Con este procedimiento tambien podemos examinar la faringe y la laringe, evaluando las cuerdas vocales, la epiglotis, la traquea y otros elementos anatomicos relacionados con la voz y la deglucion. Es especialmente util para diagnosticar disfonias, laringitis, lesiones vocales y trastornos del sueno relacionados con la respiracion.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue-50/50 to-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 border border-brand-blue-100/50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Como se realiza?</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Generalmente es bien tolerada y no requiere anestesia general. Puede realizarse en consulta externa y rara vez provoca molestias significativas. Nuestro equipo se encargara de hacer que te sientas comodo durante todo el proceso.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Al finalizar, analizamos las imagenes obtenidas y te brindamos un diagnostico preciso. Segun los resultados, te recomendaremos el tratamiento mas adecuado para mejorar tu calidad de vida.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-pink-50/50 to-white rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 border border-brand-pink-100/50">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand-pink-500 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Tu bienestar es nuestra prioridad</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            En nuestro Centro Medico, nos comprometemos a brindarte un entorno seguro y atencion personalizada. Si experimentas sintomas como ronquidos, dificultad respiratoria o cambios en tu voz, agenda una cita con nosotros. Estamos listos para ayudarte a recuperar tu bienestar.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-green-500 to-brand-green-600 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-green-glow-lg">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Â¿Necesitas un diagnostico?</h3>
          <p class="text-white/90 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
            Agenda tu cita y obtendras un diagnostico preciso con tecnologia de vanguardia.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contacto?especialidad=otorrino"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-brand-green-600 font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            Agendar consulta
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FloatingContactWidget
    doctorName="Dra. Carolina Campuzano"
    specialty="otorrinolaringologia"
    specialtyValue="Otorrinolaringologia"
  />

</PageLayout>
